{"id":8147706839348,"title":"WINDOWS: AM Auto - Mercedes Sprinter - Slider Window Sliding Door \u0026 Behind Driver","handle":"window-oem-style","description":"\u003ch3\u003eTransform Your Van with Custom Windows\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEnhance your van journey with AM Auto's tinted half slider windows. Perfect for those looking for custom van windows, AM Auto expertly crafts each window with advanced design techniques. As a result, these windows meet the highest quality standards, combining style with exceptional craftsmanship. Furthermore, they offer more than just a view; they actively transform your van into a hub of elegance and practicality.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWe Ship Promptly: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAfter you place an order, we get to work right away. We usually dispatch your window within a quick 3-5 business day period. Enjoy enhanced visibility and style for your Sprinter!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNeed an installation? \u003c\/strong\u003eNot a problem, our experienced team of technicians will be happy to help you!  Add our installation services to your order below.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch5\u003eKey Features:\u003c\/h5\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e Innovative Design:\u003c\/strong\u003e Meticulously crafted with cutting-edge design trends, these custom van windows ensure a flawless OEM style fit that enhances your van's appearance.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003ePerfect Fit:\u003c\/strong\u003e AM Auto windows integrate seamlessly into Sprinter and Transit Vans, boosting their aesthetic appeal.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eFresh Air, No Bugs:\u003c\/strong\u003e Enjoy ventilation through the expertly designed exterior screen that keeps bugs out.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eDurable and Quiet:\u003c\/strong\u003e The screen, embedded in a sturdy rubber channel, ensures durability and whisper-quiet operation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eEnhanced Security:\u003c\/strong\u003e A magnetic latch firmly secures the window, providing added safety.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003ePrivacy and UV Protection:\u003c\/strong\u003e Benefit from privacy and shield yourself from harmful UV rays with our 15% solar privacy tint safety glass.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAll in all, AMA's craftsmanship turns these custom van windows into a remarkable upgrade for your vehicle's look and functionality.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eOEM Style Windows are available for both Sprinter and Transit Vans.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2021-03-01T12:57:53-07:00","created_at":"2023-02-27T16:36:17-07:00","vendor":"AM Auto","type":"product","tags":["sprinter van 144","sprinter van 170","Windows"],"price":58900,"price_min":58900,"price_max":58900,"available":true,"price_varies":false,"compare_at_price":null,"compare_at_price_min":0,"compare_at_price_max":0,"compare_at_price_varies":false,"variants":[{"id":44560831316276,"title":"Sprinter Van \/ Driver","option1":"Sprinter Van","option2":"Driver","option3":null,"sku":"MS06-L1-HSS-P","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":{"id":44049872814388,"product_id":8147706839348,"position":2,"created_at":"2024-03-01T10:37:18-07:00","updated_at":"2024-03-01T10:39:23-07:00","alt":null,"width":3954,"height":2966,"src":"\/\/backlandgear.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/IMG_3329_35aba4f1-b633-4e19-8b2c-849b1be4c4b2.jpg?v=1709314763","variant_ids":[44560831316276]},"available":true,"name":"WINDOWS: AM Auto - Mercedes Sprinter - Slider Window Sliding Door \u0026 Behind Driver - Sprinter Van \/ Driver","public_title":"Sprinter Van \/ Driver","options":["Sprinter Van","Driver"],"price":58900,"weight":28123,"compare_at_price":null,"inventory_management":"shopify","barcode":"","featured_media":{"alt":null,"id":36481006141748,"position":2,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.333,"height":2966,"width":3954,"src":"\/\/backlandgear.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/IMG_3329_35aba4f1-b633-4e19-8b2c-849b1be4c4b2.jpg?v=1709314763"}},"requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_allocations":[],"quantity_rule":{"min":1,"max":null,"increment":1}},{"id":44560831349044,"title":"Sprinter Van \/ Passenger","option1":"Sprinter Van","option2":"Passenger","option3":null,"sku":"MS06-R1-HSS-P","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":{"id":44049872519476,"product_id":8147706839348,"position":1,"created_at":"2024-03-01T10:37:18-07:00","updated_at":"2024-03-01T10:39:23-07:00","alt":null,"width":3024,"height":4032,"src":"\/\/backlandgear.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/IMG_3342.jpg?v=1709314763","variant_ids":[44560831349044]},"available":true,"name":"WINDOWS: AM Auto - Mercedes Sprinter - Slider Window Sliding Door \u0026 Behind Driver - Sprinter Van \/ Passenger","public_title":"Sprinter Van \/ Passenger","options":["Sprinter Van","Passenger"],"price":58900,"weight":28123,"compare_at_price":null,"inventory_management":"shopify","barcode":"","featured_media":{"alt":null,"id":36481006108980,"position":1,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":0.75,"height":4032,"width":3024,"src":"\/\/backlandgear.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/IMG_3342.jpg?v=1709314763"}},"requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_allocations":[],"quantity_rule":{"min":1,"max":null,"increment":1}}],"images":["\/\/backlandgear.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/IMG_3342.jpg?v=1709314763","\/\/backlandgear.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/IMG_3329_35aba4f1-b633-4e19-8b2c-849b1be4c4b2.jpg?v=1709314763","\/\/backlandgear.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/IMG_0535.heic?v=1709314763","\/\/backlandgear.com\/cdn\/sh