                  >
                    <p><span class="metafield-multi_line_text_field">Proper storage is crucial for Tempered Glass Windows.<br />
<br />
In order to maintain the integrity of the glass, it is necessary to store the tempered glass panels in a clean, dry, and well-ventilated area, avoiding direct exposure to sunlight or heat sources. Additionally, it is important to keep the glass away from alkaline solutions, such as cement and lime, as these substances can compromise its strength and lead to a higher risk of breakage. Therefore the glass cannot be exchanged, refunded, or warrantied after leaving our location. Unless the damage occurs during shipping. In that case, a claim should be made with our shipping department, following our shipping claim procedure: shipping@backlandgear.com </span></p>
                    
