firecan-elite-fire-pit-ignik-outdoors","title":"IGNIK - FireCan Elite Portable Fire Pit","handle":"firecan-elite-fire-pit-ignik-outdoors"},"productId":8871503757620},{"lastName":"","images":[],"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"I recently installed a set of these pods and they were fantastic to work with and look great. I’ve seen a couple other manufacturers products and these are by far superior.  Don’t be afraid of laying down a good bead of urethane. It won’t squirt.","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/858F4D22-3D4E-4207-83F3-B15EEA48D171_b11ee315-0f8a-4c5c-9ac4-776670318372.jpg?v=1689301323","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/extension-pod-144-extended-depth","title":"ClimateCore: Insulated Sleeping PODS - Sprinter 144 - Extended Depth - SET","handle":"extension-pod-144-extended-depth"}],"firstName":"Matt","createdAt":"2024-06-19T15:23:33.103Z","rate":5,"productIds":[8147708215604],"countryCode":"CA","hasImages":false,"helpful":0,"first_name":"Matt","verifyBuyer":false,"status":"approved","pinned":false,"isFeatured":false,"id":"Rud5tOfGDiSf9zts4clV","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/858F4D22-3D4E-4207-83F3-B15EEA48D171_b11ee315-0f8a-4c5c-9ac4-776670318372.jpg?v=1689301323","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/extension-pod-144-extended-depth","title":"ClimateCore: Insulated Sleeping PODS - Sprinter 144 - Extended Depth - SET","handle":"extension-pod-144-extended-depth"},"productId":8147708215604},{"lastName":"Echols","images":[],"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"Super easy install.  Packaged extremely well.  Double wrapped.  Even the hardware was wrapped up nicely.  Great craftsmanship.  Excellent!","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/B44D4211-81