"first_name":"","images":[],"verified":false,"firstName":"Karafili","productIds":[8147703497012],"hasImages":false,"verifyBuyer":true,"status":"approved","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/2FBE7D9E-C221-4FC1-B30A-6293D4D2E13F_42ab09b5-29f5-4bb9-a83f-43e6f3aefe93.jpg?v=1752200841","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/side-ladder","title":"IBEX - Side Ladder High Roof Sprinter Van - Steel","handle":"side-ladder"},"productId":8147703497012},{"lastName":"Schriock","pinned":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"Much safer step than our previous step. The drop down step is also more convenient for my wife!","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/7BD34941-D9AE-4985-93BC-3AFCA03F03BC.jpg?v=1709250834","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/apex-series-rock-sliders-side-steps-drop-down-144","title":"APEX - Rock Sliders / Side Steps - 144 - Drop Down - Steel","handle":"apex-series-rock-sliders-side-steps-drop-down-144"}],"createdAt":"2024-10-05T19:35:26.361Z","rate":5,"countryCode":"US","shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","id":"yCAbskWHgRYuZxzzwb19","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"","images":[],"verified":false,"firstName":"Eldon","productIds":[9023455363380],"hasImages":false,"verifyBuyer":true,"status":"approved","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/7BD34941-D9AE-4985-93BC-3AFCA03F03BC.jpg?v=1709250834","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/apex-series-rock-sliders-side-steps-drop-down-144","title":"APEX - Rock Sliders / Side Steps - 144 - Drop Down - Steel","handle":"apex-series-rock-sliders-side-steps-drop-down-144"},"productId":9023455363380},{"lastName":"Tremblay","pinned":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"I am extremely pleased with the Backland headliner shelf. The packaging was well-prepared and quickly shipped. Not only is the shelf sturdy, it looks great and is easy to install. It even has the \"Made in Canada\" label on it. I had a few words with Darren, who was eager to help and respond to my questions. I highly recommend both this product and this company.","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/backland-interior-headliner-shelf-sprinter.webp?v=1757358265","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/overhead-shelf","title":"BACKLAND - Headliner Shelf - Sprinter","handle":"overhead-shelf"}],"createdAt":"2024-10-04T23:01:39.054Z","rate":5,"countryCode":"CA","shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","id":"QpiCXZFPqcMhgbnmaf6I","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"","images":[],"verified":false,"firstName":"Jean-François","productIds":[8702323327284],"hasImages":false,"verifyBuyer":true,"status":"approved","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/backland-interior-headliner-shelf-sprinter.webp?v=1757358265","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/overhead-shelf","title":"BACKLAND - Headliner Shelf - Sprinter","handle":"overhead-shelf"},"productId":8702323327284},{"lastName":"","images":["https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/air-reviews.appspot.com/o/submitReview%2F6NO9AZLkOG7DSYt6QgIT%2F1727998537763_IMG_1286.webp?alt=media&token=9227c8c7-3227-4530-a92e-1c013702a3e2"],"pinned":false,"verified":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"I recently installed a set of the apex steps for a wonderful client and I have to say, these are the most throughly well thought set of steps I have ever installed. I have installed roam built, owl vans, rugged design…. All of them were inferior products. They really did it right with these. \n\nThey have real usable step size a person with a normal sized foot can use, with a nice lower step option available which is the set I installed my clients were very happy with the results. They previously had the owl van steps installed and they were too small, and not particularly safe for folks with limited mobility. I can’t wait to install more backland  products as these guys won me over with these.","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_6607_3fde6449-8989-4795-8344-75e8f668438c.jpg?v=1733176755","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/rock-sliders-side-steps-sprinter-144","title":"APEX - Rock Sliders / Side Steps - 144 - Regular - Steel","handle":"rock-sliders-side-steps-sprinter-144"}],"firstName":"Ian","createdAt":"2024-10-03T23:42:28.127Z","rate":5,"productIds":[8147702481204],"countryCode":"US","hasImages":true,"shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"Ian","verifyBuyer":false,"status":"approved","id":"SbJTSRbn7KuSpHobBfhF","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_6607_3fde6449-8989-4795-8344-75e8f668438c.jpg?v=1733176755","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/rock-sliders-side-steps-sprinter-144","title":"APEX - Rock Sliders / Side Steps - 144 - Regular - Steel","handle":"rock-sliders-side-steps-sprinter-144"},"productId":8147702481204},{"lastName":"","pinned":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"I was able to get my hands on a red Bison Series Differential Skid Plate, and this product is definitely top notch! The welds, powder coating, and fit are perfect. Install was a breeze. Love all of the Backland EG products on our van!","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/B44D4211-813C-47B2-9D30-EAAA4260961E.jpg?v=1760707271","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/bison-differential-skid-plate","title":"BISON - Differential Skid Plate","handle":"bison-differential-skid-plate"}],"createdAt":"2024-10-03T21:32:03.475Z","rate":5,"countryCode":"US","shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","id":"UaeoYG4ZsfPvARhodhp7","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"","images":["https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/air-reviews.appspot.com/o/submitReview%2F6NO9AZLkOG7DSYt6QgIT%2F1727991097369_IMG_1004_jpg.webp?alt=media&token=0e11ff0c-dccc-4b75-93f3-0c5d9e7e0274"],"verified":false,"firstName":"ron.balagot@gmail.com","productIds":[8147712868660],"hasImages":true,"verifyBuyer":true,"status":"approved","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/B44D4211-813C-47B2-9D30-EAAA4260961E.jpg?v=1760707271","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/bison-differential-skid-plate","title":"BISON - Differential Skid Plate","handle":"bison-differential-skid-plate"},"productId":8147712868660},{"lastName":"Morgan","pinned":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"Picture worth a thousand words","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/ox-tire-carrier.jpg?v=1771526790","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/ox-tire-carrier","title":"OX - Tire Carrier","handle":"ox-tire-carrier"}],"createdAt":"2024-09-29T23:36:21.708Z","rate":5,"countryCode":"JP","shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","id":"bOhxdzgrcuAKIJHApmOf","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"","images":["https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/air-reviews.appspot.com/o/submitReview%2F6NO9AZLkOG7DSYt6QgIT%2F1727652945537_IMG_3693.webp?alt=media&token=b76ab4cf-3cb4-4c72-b792-9ffe9ebf2045"],"verified":false,"firstName":"Larry","productIds":[8825979535668],"hasImages":true,"verifyBuyer":true,"status":"approved","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/ox-tire-carrier.jpg?v=1771526790","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/ox-tire-carrier","title":"OX - Tire Carrier","handle":"ox-tire-carrier"},"productId":8825979535668},{"lastName":"Morgan","pinned":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"I have looked on line for other ones but these are much better","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_5409.heic?v=1716915044","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/g3-tension-strap","title":"BACKLAND - G3 Tension Strap","handle":"g3-tension-strap"}],"createdAt":"2024-09-29T23:34:43.908Z","rate":5,"countryCode":"JP","shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","id":"L5cy65kkfwi2LIWeiWgU","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"","images":[],"verified":false,"firstName":"Larry","productIds":[9090408972596],"hasImages":false,"verifyBuyer":true,"status":"approved","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_5409.heic?v=1716915044","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/g3-tension-strap","title":"BACKLAND - G3 Tension Strap","handle":"g3-tension-strap"},"productId":9090408972596},{"lastName":"","images":["https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/air-reviews.appspot.com/o/submitReview%2F6NO9AZLkOG7DSYt6QgIT%2F1726873891167_IMG_1669.webp?alt=media&token=c094a393-e1ea-4c5d-8a5f-ea8e8def9155","https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/air-reviews.appspot.com/o/submitReview%2F6NO9AZLkOG7DSYt6QgIT%2F1726873891169_IMG_1482.webp?alt=media&token=358cd591-5d67-4a4b-a264-1049384640ba"],"pinned":false,"verified":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"Purchased our OX Rear carriers for our sprinter van. The crew at Backland have always been extremely friendly and helpful. Loving our carriers. Easy to install yourself, one of the biggest if not biggest for space to add stuff to, look so good, and are sturdy. Very happy with our purchase. Will definitely purchase more from them! Can clearly tell these were designed by people who use them and took into account gear/bikes etc. \n\nAlso purchased the side steps. Brilliant addition to add accessibility to the roof without having to sacrifice one of the rear doors to a ladder.","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_0250-3.jpg?v=1769386634","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/sprinter-rear-door-storage","title":"OX - Rear Door Carrier - Sprinter","handle":"sprinter-rear-door-storage"}],"firstName":"Genna","createdAt":"2024-09-20T23:12:27.445Z","rate":5,"productIds":[8713086894388],"countryCode":"CA","hasImages":true,"shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"Genna","verifyBuyer":false,"status":"approved","id":"fLPbFCNn9LBFQW9rUIFS","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_0250-3.jpg?v=1769386634","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/sprinter-rear-door-storage","title":"OX - Rear Door Carrier - Sprinter","handle":"sprinter-rear-door-storage"},"productId":8713086894388},{"lastName":"Rudolph","pinned":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"The PODS are a quality item and coupled with the installation video, I installed them easily.  I am very happy how it all turned out!","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/64C22996-A871-4C37-AB1C-30A23A707040.jpg?v=1753382350","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/extensions-pods-170-extended-depth","title":"ClimateCore: Insulated Sleeping PODS - Sprinter 170 - Extended Depth - SET","handle":"extensions-pods-170-extended-depth"}],"createdAt":"2024-09-20T01:46:33.341Z","rate":5,"countryCode":"US","shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","id":"VPNI5bcZiOZg5a5E8GoB","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"","images":[],"verified":false,"firstName":"Constance","productIds":[8147707035956],"hasImages":false,"verifyBuyer":false,"status":"approved","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/64C22996-A871-4C37-AB1C-30A23A707040.jpg?v=1753382350","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/extensions-pods-170-extended-depth","title":"ClimateCore: Insulated Sleeping PODS - Sprinter 170 - Extended Depth - SET","handle":"extensions-pods-170-extended-depth"},"productId":8147707035956},{"lastName":"","images":[],"pinned":false,"verified":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"I bought a set of the Drop down rocker steps - they look cool - the Indy coating is very grippy and feel very safe on them. Install was very straight forward. They are a bit heavy which i think is a good thing - super solid and will likely take any abuse I put them through. I'm glad there is a drop down version. The extra inches make it a lot easier for my wife to get in and out. Without the drop down, I would have needed to choose another solution. Bought these with rear bumper and so everything matches up nicely\n\nHarrison","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/7BD34941-D9AE-4985-93BC-3AFCA03F03BC.jpg?v=1709250834","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/apex-series-rock-sliders-side-steps-drop-down-144","title":"APEX - Rock Sliders / Side Steps - 144 - Drop Down - Steel","handle":"apex-series-rock-sliders-side-steps-drop-down-144"}],"firstName":"Harrison","createdAt":"2024-09-14T16:00:50.226Z","rate":5,"productIds":[9023455363380],"countryCode":"US","hasImages":false,"shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"Harrison","verifyBuyer":false,"status":"approved","id":"dLiID3igwQC4ICKdnjfm","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/7BD34941-D9AE-4985-93BC-3AFCA03F03BC.jpg?v=1709250834","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/apex-series-rock-sliders-side-steps-drop-down-144","title":"APEX - Rock Sliders / Side Steps - 144 - Drop Down - Steel","handle":"apex-series-rock-sliders-side-steps-drop-down-144"},"productId":9023455363380},{"lastName":"Li","pinned":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"I purchased this bumper for my Sprinter 3500XD. When it arrived I discovered that it didn't fit due to the more narrow frame rails on the 3500 and thus narrower factory hitch. The team at Backland were very eager to help me solve the problem and came up with a bracket that would allow it to fit my 3500 factory hitch. That is what I call customer service. The bumper is robust and the Indy coating makes it super grippy. I also bought their Rock Slider side steps so everything matches up nicely. Love the innovation.  Only request is more parts for the 3500 but i know there are fewer of us out there.\n\nThanks\n\nHarrison","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_5585.jpg?v=1760486710","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/apex-series-rear-bumper-step","title":"APEX - Rear Step Bumper - Steel","handle":"apex-series-rear-bumper-step"}],"createdAt":"2024-09-14T15:50:53.121Z","rate":5,"countryCode":"US","shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","id":"HLkikhSHwI27MFGJrBpD","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"","images":[],"verified":false,"firstName":"Harrison","productIds":[8147710279988],"hasImages":false,"verifyBuyer":true,"status":"approved","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_5585.jpg?v=1760486710","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/apex-series-rear-bumper-step","title":"APEX - Rear Step Bumper - Steel","handle":"apex-series-rear-bumper-step"},"productId":8147710279988},{"lastName":"Bulman","pinned":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"Great little portable fire pit for our van. Amazing heat off of this thing. Backland's price includes the lava rocks - definitely makes a more enjoyable fire with better heat radiation. We're getting tons of use this season with all the fire bans. Highly recommend!","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_8971.jpg?v=1734277253","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/firecan-elite-fire-pit-ignik-outdoors","title":"IGNIK - FireCan Elite Portable Fire Pit","handle":"firecan-elite-fire-pit-ignik-outdoors"}],"createdAt":"2024-08-19T22:21:25.222Z","rate":5,"countryCode":"CA","shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","id":"4ecVpyE0GbyZjgUnzwo5","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"","images":[],"verified":false,"firstName":"Joe","productIds":[8871503757620],"hasImages":false,"verifyBuyer":true,"status":"approved","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_8971.jpg?v=1734277253","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/firecan-elite-fire-pit-ignik-outdoors","title":"IGNIK - FireCan Elite Portable Fire Pit","handle":"firecan-elite-fire-pit-ignik-outdoors"},"productId":8871503757620}],"carouselReviews":[{"