1753382350","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/extensions-pods-170-extended-depth","title":"ClimateCore: Insulated Sleeping PODS - Sprinter 170 - Extended Depth - SET","handle":"extensions-pods-170-extended-depth"},"productId":8147707035956},{"firstName":"George Sutton","lastName":"","images":["https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/air-reviews.appspot.com/o/submitReview%2F6NO9AZLkOG7DSYt6QgIT%2F1753223052933_IMG_3789.webp?alt=media&token=0d566366-4610-452b-9eae-e277f2aa4fc8","https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/air-reviews.appspot.com/o/submitReview%2F6NO9AZLkOG7DSYt6QgIT%2F1753223083327_IMG_5116.webp?alt=media&token=116db968-5466-4c87-9637-09b11dfc9e70"],"rate":5,"content":"We had Backland install the standard rock sliders 6 months ago on our ‘24 170AWD and we couldn’t be happier.  These are incredibly stout, stylish and offer unbeatable protection.  The Indy coating seems nearly bulletproof, offering great grip without sacrificing barefoot walkability. Highly recommended","variants":[],"first_name":"George Sutton","last_name":"","shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_6863_35116538-aa71-40a4-8336-dd2c6bc3dcc1.jpg?v=1751665040","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/rock-sliders-side-steps-steel-170","title":"APEX - Rock Sliders / Side Steps - 170 - Regular - Steel","handle":"rock-sliders-side-steps-steel-170"}],"productIds":[8147705069876],"verifyBuyer":false,"countryCode":"US","helpful":0,"notHelpful":0,"hasImages":true,"verified":false,"source":"Writed by customer","pinned":false,"isFeatured":false,"status":"approved","createdAt":"2025-07-22T22:25:59.739Z","id":"KlnEMBM5NMJWmTkxMxkK","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_6863_35116538-aa71-40a4-8336-dd2c6bc3dcc1.jpg?v=1751665040","productLink