s easy to install. It even has the \"Made in Canada\" label on it. I had a few words with Darren, who was eager to help and respond to my questions. I highly recommend both this product and this company.","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/backland-interior-headliner-shelf-sprinter.webp?v=1757358265","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/overhead-shelf","title":"BACKLAND - Headliner Shelf - Sprinter","handle":"overhead-shelf"}],"createdAt":"2024-10-04T23:01:39.054Z","rate":5,"countryCode":"CA","shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","id":"QpiCXZFPqcMhgbnmaf6I","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"","images":[],"verified":false,"firstName":"Jean-François","productIds":[8702323327284],"hasImages":false,"verifyBuyer":true,"status":"approved","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/backland-interior-headliner-shelf-sprinter.webp?v=1757358265","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/overhead-shelf","title":"BACKLAND - Headliner Shelf - Sprinter","handle":"overhead-shelf"},"productId":8702323327284},{"lastName":"","images":["https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/air-reviews.appspot.com/o/submitReview%2F6NO9AZLkOG7DSYt6QgIT%2F1727998537763_IMG_1286.webp?alt=media&token=9227c8c7-3227-4530-a92e-1c013702a3e2"],"pinned":false,"verified":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"I recently installed a set of the apex steps for a wonderful client and I have to say, these are the most throughly well thought set of steps I have ever installed. I have installed roam built, owl vans, rugged design…. All of them were inferior products. They really did it right with these. \n\nThey have real usable step size a person with a normal sized foot can use, with a nice lower step option available which is the set I installed my clients were very happy with the results. They previously had the owl van steps installed and they were too small, and not particularly safe for folks with limited mobility. I can’t wait to install more backland  products as these guys won me over with these.","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_6607_3fde6449-8989-4795-8344-75e8f668438c.jpg?v=1733176755","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/rock-sliders-side-steps-sprinter-144","title":"APEX - Rock Sliders / Side Steps - 144 - Regular - Steel","handle":"rock-sliders-side-steps-sprinter-144"}],"firstName":"Ian","createdAt":"2024-10-03T23:42:28.127Z","rate":5,"productIds":[8147702481204],"countryCode":"US","hasImages":true,"shopDomain":"backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com","helpful":0,"isFeatured":false,"first_name":"Ian","verifyBuyer":false,"status":"approved","id":"SbJTSRbn7KuSpHobBfhF","isProductExists":true,"statusBeforeTrash":"disapproved","product":{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/IMG_6607_3fde6449-8989-4795-8344-75e8f668438c.jpg?v=1733176755","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/rock-sliders-side-steps-sprinter-144","title":"APEX - Rock Sliders / Side Steps - 144 - Regular - Steel","handle":"rock-sliders-side-steps-sprinter-144"},"productId":8147702481204},{"lastName":"","pinned":false,"notHelpful":0,"variants":[],"source":"Writed by customer","content":"I was able to get my hands on a red Bison Series Differential Skid Plate, and this product is definitely top notch! The welds, powder coating, and fit are perfect. Install was a breeze. Love all of the Backland EG products on our van!","products":[{"image":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0732/4208/3636/files/B44D4211-813C-47B2-9D30-EAAA4260961E.jpg?v=1760707271","productLink":"https://backland-expedition-gear.myshopify.com/products/bison-differential-skid-plate","title":"BISON - Differential Skid Plate","handle":"bison-d