here you need it.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard;\"><em>Please note: The frame will not be pre-installed, and the hole for the frame(s) must be cut while the roof rack is mounted on the van. This ensures accurate placement and helps minimize the risk of errors during installation.</em></p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard;\">Additional Frames and Custom Sizes Available: If you need more fan openings, we offer custom-made frames to your exact specifications.</p>","type":"paragraph","text_en":"<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard;\">Purchase a Roof Rack&nbsp;<strong>frame for a fan opening (20\" x 27\")</strong>, compatible with popular models like the Maxxair or AirPlus fans, allowing you to add ventilation exactly where you need it.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard;\"><em>Please note: The frame will not be pre-installed, and the hole for the frame(s) must be cut while the roof rack is mounted on the van. This ensures accurate placement and helps minimize the risk of errors during installation.</em></p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard;\">Additional Frames and Custom Sizes Available: If you need more fan openings, we offer custom-made frames to your exact specifications.</p>","columnWidth":100},{"id":"image-swatches-3","type":"image-swatches","label":"Additional Cut-outs","style":"vertical","helptext":"Click image to select","label_en":"Additional Cut-outs","columnWidth":100,"helptext_en":"Click image to select","image_width":"120","scroll_type":"default","hidden_label":true,"image_height":"100","initial_state":"expand","label_on_cart":"Additional Cut-outs"